snippet.title: reverse Snake - Xbox One / Windows 10 Gameplay
snippet.description:
simple classic game of snake, but with a twist.
you control the food and try not to get eaten or touch the red hot lava walls.
survive for 4 minutes and win or die trying

a modern take on classic snake were
you control the food.
you control the difficulty.
you, control the game.

Developed by Atom Technologies
Footage is from the Windows 10 version
